summary: AN ORDINANCE vacating the south 187 feet of the alley adjacent to Lots 17-24 between Block 51 and Block 52, Boston Company's Plat of West Seattle; accepting a Deed for Alley Purposes and placing the real property conveyed by such deed under the jurisdiction of the Seattle Department of Transportation; laying off, opening, widening, extending, and establishing that portion of Block 51 and Block 52, Boston Company's Plat of West Seattle; and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement as reflected in Clerk File 307032.
